        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Course Materials and Faculty Records series is divided into four subseries: Structures I; Structures II; Miscellaneous Topical Files, and Administrative Files. All topical files are arranged alphabetically. This series contains educational material utilized by Werner in the classroom, such as coursepacks and lecture notes for two of his courses. Topical files contain sketches and example problems relating to various architectural concepts, such as flexure, force, and load. The Administrative Files subseries contains additional material regarding Werner's professional history and his retirement from the University of Michigan.</p>
